<AbstractNarration>The Evaluators' Institute provides high-quality short-courses taught by nationally recognized experts in the evaluation field.  Courses are scheduled to allow participants to take 2-3 courses over the period of a week.  This SGER will test whether SMET professionals can be involved in these courses by offering $1000 Tuition scholarships.  Since the Evaluators' Institute is providing courses this summer and a limited set again in the fall, decisions about future planning by the Evaluation Program can be made in a timely manner.</AbstractNarration>
